    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a Jujutsu Sorcerer, you gain the following class features.</p><h3>Hit Points</h3><p><strong>Hit Dice</strong>: 1d10 per Jujutsu Sorcerer level<br /><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level and beyond</strong>: 10 + your constitution modifier</p><hr /><h3>Chakra Points</h3><p><strong>Chakra Dice</strong>: 1d8 per Jujutsu Sorcerer level<br /><strong>Chakra Points at 1st Level</strong>: 8 + your constitution modifier<br /><strong>Chakra Points at Higher Levels</strong>: 1d8 (or 5) + your Constitution Modifier per Jujutsu Sorcerer level after 1st.</p><hr /><h3>Proficiencies</h3><p><strong>Armor</strong>: Light armor, medium armor<br /><strong>Weapons</strong>: All Simple and Martial Weapons and One exotic of your choice<br /><strong>Ninja Tools</strong>: Tracking Kit and Forensics Kit<br /><strong>Saving Throws</strong>: Charisma, Constitution, Dexterity<br /><strong>Skills</strong>: Acrobatics, Chakra Control Choose any 2 from the following: Insight, Perception, Athletics, Sleight of Hand, Intimidation, Investigation, History, Stealth, Survival</p><h1>Jujutsu Sorcerer Advancement</h1><table><thead><tr><th>Level</th><th>Proficiency Bonus</th><th>Features</th><th>Cursed Energy</th><th>Cursed Techniques</th><th>Jutsu Known</th><th>Highest Rank Jutsu Known</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1st</td><td>+3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.t7-class.Item.ZSpS9XwuYzaD0iZJ]{Cursed Energy}, @UUID[Compendium.n5eb.t7-class.Item.Y4Pjg5tgkmxNFc7X]{Cursed Technique}, @UUID[Compendium.n5eb.t7-class.Item.va8ZrcgNQumh2ivr]{Binding Vow}</td><td>6</td><td>2</td><td>6</td><td>D-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>2nd</td><td>+3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.t7-class.Item.ku4uRjtIU7CKcUAQ]{The Zone}, @UUID[Compendium.n5eb.t7-class.Item.B63gGyvdd5iGEG5W]{Exorcism of the Wicked}</td><td>7</td><td>2</td><td>6</td><td>D-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>3rd</td><td>+3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.t7-class.Item.tLsSNIGxUsSFPHDZ]{Jujutsu Technique}, @UUID[Compendium.n5eb.t7-class.Item.Y4Pjg5tgkmxNFc7X]{Cursed Technique (2)}</td><td>8</td><td>3</td><td>7</td><td>D-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>4th</td><td>+4</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.3R6ULWi6YDL3qyIf]{Ability Score Improvement}</td><td>9</td><td>3</td><td>7</td><td>D-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>5th</td><td>+4</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.t7-class.Item.5xh5AzxSqcgvbkfd]{Extra Attack}</td><td>10</td><td>3</td><td>8</td><td>C-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>6th</td><td>+4</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.t7-class.Item.Y4Pjg5tgkmxNFc7X]{Cursed Technique (3)}, @UUID[Compendium.n5eb.t7-class.Item.WcgJ8L0sCzp6if4w]{Ever Vigilant}</td><td>11</td><td>4</td><td>8</td><td>C-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>7th</td><td>+5</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.t7-class.Item.tLsSNIGxUsSFPHDZ]{Jujutsu Technique (2)}</td><td>12</td><td>4</td><td>9</td><td>C-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>8th</td><td>+5</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.3R6ULWi6YDL3qyIf]{Ability Score Improvement}</td><td>13</td><td>4</td><td>9</td><td>C-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>9th</td><td>+5</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.t7-class.Item.URN6xqebcUNE5gtB]{Cursed Physique}</td><td>14</td><td>4</td><td>10</td><td>B-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>10th</td><td>+6</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.t7-class.Item.ZSpS9XwuYzaD0iZJ]{Cursed Energy (2)}</td><td>15</td><td>4</td><td>10</td><td>B-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>11th</td><td>+6</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.t7-class.Item.tLsSNIGxUsSFPHDZ]{Jujutsu Technique (3)}</td><td>16</td><td>4</td><td>11</td><td>B-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>12th</td><td>+6</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.class.Item.3R6ULWi6YDL3qyIf]{Ability Score Improvement}</td><td>17</td><td>4</td><td>11</td><td>B-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>13th</td><td>+7</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.t7-class.Item.B63gGyvdd5iGEG5W]{Exorcism of the Wicked (2)}</td><td>18</td><td>4</td><td>12</td><td>A-Rank</td></tr><tr><td>14th</td><td>+7</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.n5eb.t7-class.Item.Y4Pjg5tgkmxNFc7X]{Cursed Technique (4)}, @UUID[Compendium.n5eb.t7-class.Item.IAd3jkO2XhCvAQYg]{Pseudo-Skilled}</td><td>19</td><td>5</td><td>12</td><td>A-Rank</td></tr><tr>